    3001 [label="SPDXLicense:\nThis license is BSD-2-Clause with the MIT disclaimer. The linux kernel uses this\nlicense extensively throughout the driver subsystem since 2005. Note that the\nOpenIB.org license is a true match to BSD-2-Clause."
